name: Add item in Shopping Cart
description:
I need to add item in Shopping Cart as an user in Magazine Luiza e-commerce.
   It`s also necessary to validate the item in Shopping Cart.

elements.name: Access Magazine Luiza and search product.

steps.name: access magazine luiza homepage
search a product
it must be a list of products found
select first product
select to add in Shopping Cart
select to continue without extended warranty
product must be in Shopping Cart.
